{"lang": "ja_JP", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "安らかな譫言", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-4", "avgTag": "戦闘後", "storyName": "客間の迷宮", "storyInfo": "エイヤフィヤトラに励まされた初華は、ついに島を出て祥子を探しに行くことを決心する。祥子も初華のいた別荘までたどり着いたが、初華はすでにそこから出発しており、二人はすれ違うことになった。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同じことを何度も繰り返せば、その行為はやがて無意識下に沈んでいく。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同じ一日を何度も繰り返せば、その循環に閉じ込められてしまうのだ。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自覚することも、そこから抜け出すこともできない。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長く、果てしなく続く、覚めることのない夢のように。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_hotel", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "山にこだまする羽獣のさえずりと共に、毎朝自然と目が覚める。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二度寝したければ、再び顔を枕に埋めればいい。ここには彼女を急かす者などいないのだから。"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g6_noblelivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布団とベッドを整えたら、キッチンで簡単な朝食を作る。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "パン、目玉焼き、ミルク……"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何を食べるも、何を飲むも、すべて自分の気分次第だ。"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ひとりピアノの傍に腰かけ、鍵盤を叩く。弦を調律して少しずつ正確な音に合わせていき、一つの音を整えると、また次の弦に手を伸ばす。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後の弦の調律が終わる頃には、また最初の弦が狂い始めていた。"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうして、もう一度調律を繰り返す。"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "38_g21_skystarry_L1/38_g21_skystarry_R1/38_g21_skystarry_L2/38_g21_skystarry_R2", "solidwidth": "1280/1280/1280/1280", "solidheight": "720/720/720/720", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 60.0, "yFrom": 720.0, "yTo": 360.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ひとり真夏の草原に寝転がり、満天の星空を眺める。"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華は知っている。星はたとえ昨日と同じ位置にあるように見えても、実はほんの僅かに動き続けていることを。"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今でこそ、隣り合う二つの星は人々から何らかの意味を与えられている。しかし何千万年も経てば、二つの星は遥か遠くへと離れ、完全な「他人」となる。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人と人の関係と同じように。"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今日も、あの子は帰ってこなかった。"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ひと気のない小島で、脳裏に残った微かな記憶だけを頼りに、不確かな夢を築く。"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記憶の牢獄に囚われる。人形のように。"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執着と絶望が身体を満たし、どこまでも膨れ上がっていく。"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華は、この島から動けなかった。"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g6_noblelivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初めは、ただふらっと散歩に行っただけだと思ってた。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後になって、港で働いてる人たちから聞いたんだ。あの子が一人で島を出る船に乗ってたって……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どうして探しに行かないんですか？", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "こんな一日をもう何度も繰り返してきたからね。これが夢か現実かも分からなくなるくらい。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私は……もうあの子の顔も、名前も、よく思い出せなくなっちゃった。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "きっとここが私の終着点……だから、ここで静かに待ち続けるよ。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "私は待ってる。あの子が帰ってくる日か、私の命が尽きる日を。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "悲しみの泉はいつか枯れ果てる。涙が出なくなれば、泣くこともできなくなる。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "誰も気に留めないこんな隅っこが、私に一番ふさわしい居場所なんだよ。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "「ダメです！」", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 28.0, "delay": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#8$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "――！", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#8$2"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華さん、泣いてるってことは、まだその人への想いは残ってるってことですよね？", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "こんなの、あなたが望んだ結末じゃないですよね！？", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "エイヤフィヤトラ", "content": "せめて……"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "エイヤフィヤトラ", "content": "せめてその方に面と向かって、あなたの気持ちを伝えるべきです。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#7$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#7$2"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私にだって分かったんです。初華さんの気持ちは、きっとその人にも伝わります。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "全力で叫ばないと、彼女の心に届きませんよ？", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼女を知らない私にも気持ちが伝わったんですから。同じように、きっと彼女にも伝えられるはずです。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#7$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あの子に……でも、あなたを一人にするわけには――", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#7$2"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私なら大丈夫です。なんといってもロドスの訓練を受けたオペレーターですから。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "たまたま知り合っただけの私に、初華さんはとても優しくしてくれました。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今度は、あなた自身の心に問いかけるべきです――今この瞬間、どうしたいのかって。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小声）あの子に会いたい……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#14$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……ううん、何でもない。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華さん、私、唇が読めるんですよ。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "「ほら　逃げられないわ」", "x": 300.0, "y": 220.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n「弱っていく君　閉じ込めて」", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n「you know i want...」", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n「i want... i want...」", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n「i want you so... i want...」", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g5_siestaunbuiltland_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstprun", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "srun"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "srun", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "気付いた時には、初華は全力で駆け出していた。"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胸の奥が、今までにないほど火照っているのを感じる。ふらふらと目眩を覚えるほどに。"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "しかし最後に残った理性が、絶えず初華の耳に囁き続ける――"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "名前も、顔もよく思い出せないのに……", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "この広大な大地で、どうやって彼女を見つけるつもり？", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それでもあの子に会いたいの！", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何があっても、もう一度あの子に会いたい――！", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "その声は初華自身よりも先に、心が向かう先へと響き渡っていく。"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そして初華は、自分の声を追うように全力で駆け抜けていった。"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "srun", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g6_noblelivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子は別荘へと辿り着いた。その中は、すべてがモーフィアスに見せられたものと全く同じだった。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華――", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "間取りも、調度品も……棚の中の本さえまったく一緒……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どうして……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "床には塵一つなく、キッチンには二人では使いきれない数の食器が並び、ダイニングには十人以上が座れる長テーブルまで置かれている。"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華がここで一人暮らしする光景を、祥子は想像できなかった。"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢の中なら、辛い思い出なんて捨ててしまえばいいのに……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "きっと、二人にとってはすごく大切な場所だと思ってたんでしょうね。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あなたがこの別荘の家主さんですね……初華さんはついさっき出て行ってしまいました。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……どちらへ行きましたの？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼女はようやく自分の本心に気づき、あなたを探しに行くことを決めました。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g3_islandharbor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船に乗るのかい？", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はい、この島を出ます。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうかい、なら出航まで少し待ってな。乗客がもう一人来るはずなんだ。", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あの嬢ちゃん、まだ戻らないのか……捜してる人が見つかってるといいんだが。", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大丈夫です、待つのは慣れて……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華はその先の言葉を無理やり飲み込んだが、船長はそれを気にも留めなかった。"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はぁ……夜の海は波も高いし霧も濃いから、船を出すのは危険なんだ。乗客の安全が最優先だってのによ！", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shipbell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あぁ、通信塔からの信号が来やがったか。さっさと出ろって急かしてやがる。", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "65_i05_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.15, "yScale": 1.15, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.15, "yScaleFrom": 1.15, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 15.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あの塔の上にいる人、旗を振ってる……", "name": "三角初華"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふん、あの飲んだくれは俺が毎月くれてやるビールで生きてるようなもんさ。", "name": "親切な船長"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「航海の無事を祈る。あと、俺のビールを忘れるんじゃないぞ。」……か。", "name": "親切な船長"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふん、あいつの酒だけは忘れねぇよ！", "name": "親切な船長"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船長はそう言うと、船に飛び乗った。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shipwhistle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海から吹きつける風に乗って、小さな島の隅々にまで汽笛が響き渡る。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "美しい思い出と辛い思い出が詰まった島を眺めながら、初華は頭に様々な言葉を浮かべていた。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……私のこと、忘れないでね。", "name": "三角初華"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "忘れることなんて、できるはずがない。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "子供の頃からここで一緒に暮らしていた。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "きっと、もう一度会えると信じてる――", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_keeprunning", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "step", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "step", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華――！", "name": "豊川祥子"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はぁ……はぁ……けほっ、けほっ……", "name": "豊川祥子"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "65_i05_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "う……初華……！", "name": "豊川祥子"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_harbor_busy", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "かすれた声で名前を呼ぶ。"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "返事はなく、ただ打ち寄せる波の音のみが返ってくる。"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船はすでに島を去っていた。"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今、彼女一人だけが取り残された。"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g4_islandharbor_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_strangeclap", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "数えきれないほどの日々を待ち続けた少女は、ついに友人を探す旅へと踏み出すことを決意した。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "――けど、まさか最後の最後ですれ違っちゃうなんて……あーあ、とっても残念。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正直、あの子が出て行くとは思わなかったわ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私が用意した結末では、あの子はあんたのことなんて全部忘れて、平穏な一生を送るはずだったんだけど。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あんたが彼女に与える影響を過小評価していたわ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "認めてあげる、今回は引き分けよ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "でも残念ね。あのスピードだと、船はもうすぐ沈んじゃうわ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "え……？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここは私の作る夢なのよ。この島一つ作るだけでも大変なのに、まさかテラ全土を作れって言うの？　あんたたちの悲しい茶番劇を、この大地全てを再現して何度も上演しろって言うわけ？", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船はもうすぐ夢の境界に突き当たるわ。そして彼女はまた、次の夢に落ちていくの。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何度も繰り返して、何度もリセットされて……", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いつかあなたの存在も忘れちゃうのよ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そんな……何とかして追いつかないと――", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$2"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "もう遅いわ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子は足元に冷たい感触を覚えた。いつの間にか、海水がくるぶしまでを浸していたのだ。"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふと見上げると、海と空の間は暗雲で覆われており、そこに時折鋭い閃光が走っていた。"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華――！", "name": "豊川祥子"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海水が狂ったような速さで満ちていく。祥子は何者かに深淵へと引き摺り込まれていくように感じた。"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華、待ってて――", "name": "豊川祥子"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g12_diving", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_underwtr", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "u"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "u", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暗くて、冷たくて、息ができない。"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海水が両耳の鼓膜を圧迫する。空からの微かな光が薄れていくのと同時に、胸に残ったわずかな酸素が尽きていく。"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "視界がどんどん霞んでいく。力を失って開いた口に苦い海水が流れ込み、最後に残った意識すら呑み込んでいった。"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そのまま、ずっと、ずっと沈んでいく。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海の底、光の届かない場所まで。"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "u", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「祥……」"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「祥……祥……！」"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どこからともなく、声が近付いてくる。"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "ここはどこ？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "わたくしを呼ぶ、この声は――", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥……祥、起きて……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "懐かしい声。ずっと聞いていなかった声。"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冷たい水で満ちた海底は跡形もなく消えた。その代わりに、乾いた地面と、空中を舞う砂埃が目に映る。"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "この声は……", "name": "豊川祥子"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "65_i06", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "type": "cg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子がやっとの思いで瞼を開くと、淡い色をした髪が目に入った。"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "type": "cg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥、大丈夫？", "name": "若葉睦"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……睦？", "name": "豊川祥子"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うん。", "name": "若葉睦"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何の変哲もないその返事に、祥子は涙が止まらなかった。"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それは決して、砂埃のせいではなかった。祥子は、自分がどれだけ心細さを感じていたかを理解していた。"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いま話すと涙声になってしまう。だが、そんなことは気にしていられなかった。目の前にいる唯一の希望に縋るしかなかったのだ。"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦……わたくし……どうすればいいんですの……", "name": "豊川祥子"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}